}
</code></pre>

<p>Then the zend xmlrpc client got a Fatal error:</p>

<p>Fatal error: Uncaught exception 'Zend_XmlRpc_Client_FaultException' with message 'Failed to parse response' in Z:\working\www\foobar\Zend\XmlRpc\Client.php:348 Stack trace: #0 Z:\working\www\foobar\foobar.php(4): Zend_XmlRpc_Client-&gt;call('foobar.bar') #1 {main} thrown in Z:\working\www\foobar\Zend\XmlRpc\Client.php on line 348</p>

<p>And this code:</p>

<pre><code>public int bar() {
    return 1234567890;
}
</code></pre>

